ive-cynthia-ervivo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/live-cynthia-ervivo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>辛西娅·埃里沃（Cynthia Erivo）否认声称她打算在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">2025年的奥斯卡颁奖典礼</a>上表演<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wicked"><em>邪恶的</em></a>歌曲，并说这个想法就像“一厢情愿”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/oscars-2025-nominations-full-list-3831350">奥斯卡2025提名 - 请参阅完整列表</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年的仪式<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-2025-oscars-will-not-include-performances-for-best-original-song-category-3831285">将不包括最佳原创歌曲类别的现场表演</a>，在该类别中提名的艺术家将在整个晚上演出，以获得颁奖典礼。取而代之的是，该节目引起了歌曲作者的“个人思考”的关注。</p><p>尽管大多数奥斯卡提名都在今年早些时候透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/elton-john-pharrell-williams-trent-reznor-among-oscars-2025-shortlist-for-best-original-song-3823258">但最佳原创歌曲和最佳原创乐谱的入围名单在12月揭幕</a>。在最佳原创歌曲入围名单的艺术家中，有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">Elton John</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pharrell-williams">Pharrell Williams</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/trent-reznor">Trent Reznor</a>和Atticus Ross， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a>等。</p><p>几个主要的大片在入围名单中列出了最佳原始得分，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/gladiator-2"><em>角斗士2</em></a> ，<em>挑战者</em>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/beetlejuice-beetlejuice"><em>贝特利朱吉斯·贝特利朱吉斯</em></a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/alien-romulus"><em>《外星人：romulus：Romulus》</em></a>和《 Erivo Starring <em>Wicked》</em> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3756649" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3756649" style="width: 1317px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3756649" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/wicked-Ariana-grande.jpg" alt="邪恶" width="1317" height="836" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/wicked-Ariana-grande.jpg 1317w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/wicked-Ariana-grande-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/wicked-Ariana-grande-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/wicked-Ariana-grande-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/wicked-Ariana-grande-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1317px) 100vw, 1317px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3756649" class="wp-caption-text"> Ariana Grande和Cynthia Erivo在“邪恶”中。图片来源：环球影城。</figcaption></figure><p>昨晚（2月7日），她在批评家选择奖的红地毯上与<a href="https://variety.com/2025/film/news/cynthia-erivo-denies-wicked-performance-oscars-1236301048/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>综艺节目</em></a>进行了交谈，鉴于该学院希望通过自己和联合主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">Ariana Grande</a>表演的<em>邪恶</em>数字的混音打开电视转播。</p><p> “为什么每个人都说这句话？当被问及报告时，她说。 “这对我个人来说就像一厢情愿。我们为什么要唱歌？”</p><p>当被问及她是否与学院谈论表演时，她很快就否认了这一点。 “不！” Erivo回答说：“人们问我是否要在奥斯卡颁奖典礼上唱歌。我不知道为什么我们会这样做，因为我们的歌没有提名。那不会发生。我不知道该告诉你什么。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFy4ES5JFlo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0