</a> ），Demi Moore（<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-substance"><i>物质</i></a>）和Fernanda Torres（<i>我还在这里</i>）竞争。</p><p>这位演员最近承认， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cynthia-erivo-uncontrollably-wept-when-she-saw-herself-in-wicked-3827651">当她第一次在电影中的屏幕上看到自己时，她“无法控制地哭泣”</a> ，并补充说，她现在在首映和电影上映之前总共看到了9次。</p><p> “我第一次看到它的时候，我完全不知所措，我认为我的大脑完全被遮住了，” Erivo说。 “我从电影中抹去了自己。我当时想，“我不认为我在那儿。我不认为我在那里。”</p><p>最近，奥斯卡提名人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cynthia-erivo-says-rada-refused-to-let-her-do-westlife-job-it-was-a-weird-looking-down-on-a-backing-vocals-gig-3832361">透露，伦敦市中心皇家艺术学院的Rada曾经阻止她在</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/westlife">Westlife</a>的工作，因为他们“低头看着”了Backing Vocals演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cynthia-erivo-denies-wicked-oscars-performance-rumours-this-feels-like-wishful-thinking-to-me-3836197">辛西娅·埃里沃（Cynthia Erivo）否认“邪恶”的奥斯卡表演谣言：“这对我来说就像是一厢情愿的想法”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
大卫·林奇（David Lynch）的死因已揭示https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynchs-cause-of-death-has-been-revealed-3836185?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=david-lynchs-cause-of-death-has-被剥离Poppy BurtonSat, 08 Feb 2025 08:43:50 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3836185 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="大卫·林奇（David Lynch）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>心爱的后期导演的死是他的家人于一月份在社交媒体上宣布的</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynchs-cause-of-death-has-been-revealed-3836185">大卫·林奇（David Lynch）的死因已被揭示出</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="大卫·林奇（David Lynch）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-lynch">大卫·林奇（David Lynch</a> ）的死因已揭示。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/david-lynch-obituary-twin-peaks-3829834">大卫·林奇（David Lynch） -  1946  -  2025年：一个真正有远见的电影</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-dies-aged-78-3829681">他的家人在今年早些时候（1月16日）在社交媒体上宣布了备受喜爱的后期导演的死亡</a>- 他年龄在78岁。林奇（Lynch）<em>因穆霍兰德（Mulholland Drive）</em> ，<em>蓝色天鹅绒</em>和标志性的电视连续剧<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/twin-peaks"><em>Twin Peaks</em></a>等电影而闻名，他透露了他的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynchs-health-problems-mean-he-can-no-longer-direct-in-person-3781105">口感</a>去年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynchs-health-problems-mean-he-can-no-longer-direct-in-person-3781105">诊断</a>是由于他一生中大部分吸烟引起的。 11月，他分享说他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-now-requires-supplemental-oxygen-to-walk-its-a-big-price-to-pay-3812940">需要补充氧气行走</a>。</p><p>据推测， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/la-music-community-tragic-wildfires-long-lasting-effects-3828259">洛杉矶野火</a>影响了他的健康状况，匿名消息人士告诉<a href="https://deadline.com/2025/01/david-lynch-dead-twin-peaks-blue-velvet-elephant-man-1236258625/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Deadline，</em></a>他的健康情况变得更糟，因为他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-reportedly-died-after-being-forced-to-relocate-from-his-house-due-to-la-wildfires-3829793">被迫从洛杉矶的Sunset Boulevard撤离家乡</a>。</p><p>现在， <a href="https://www.tmz.com/2025/02/07/david-lynch-cause-of-death-cardiac-arrest/#continued" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>TMZ</em></a>报道说，<em>橡皮头</em>局长因心脏骤停而死亡，慢性阻塞性肺部疾病被认为是根本原因。该出版物获得的文件是洛杉矶县公共卫生部在星期五（2月7日）发布的死亡证明，也将脱水视为重要因素。 </p><figure id="attachment_3836189" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3836189" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3836189" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-directing.jpg" alt="大卫·林奇（David Lynch）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-directing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-directing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-directing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-directing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-directing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/david-lynch-directing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3836189" class="wp-caption-text">林奇（Lynch）透过Panavision Panaflex电影摄像机，指导街头野外拍摄的拍摄。信用：艾西·哈珀（Acey Harper）/盖蒂图像）</figcaption></figure><p>林奇（Lynch）过去了，他的家人在第二天打破了新闻，并在他的Facebook页面上写道：“现在他不再与我们在一起，世界上有一个大漏洞。但是，正如他会说的那样，“请关注甜甜圈，而不是在孔上”。这是美好的一天，一路有金色的阳光和蓝天。”</p><p>后来，他们被迫<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynchs-family-slam-bullshit-reports-of-memorial-service-its-hurtful-3831619">否认宣称社交媒体关于林奇的亲密朋友和合作者等吉尔·麦克拉克兰（Kyle Maclachlan）和劳拉·德恩（Laura Dern）的合作者的葬礼</a>。他们写道：“我为人们为此而飞来飞去，我觉得有人发布这种废话是如此错误。” “这很伤心。请向任何发布这些谎言的人投诉。”</p><p>自林奇（Lynch）逝世以来，娱乐行业的致敬涌入。传奇导演<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/steven-spielberg-pays-tribute-to-david-lynch-an-original-and-unique-voice-3829853">史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格（Steven Spielberg）</a>将他描述为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/steven-spielberg-pays-tribute-to-david-lynch-an-original-and-unique-voice-3829853">“原始而独特的声音”</a> ，回想起他们在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/the-fabelmans-review-steven-spielberg-3387525"><em>法布尔曼斯（Fabelmans）</em></a>上的作品。</p><p>在其他向林奇致敬的名人中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/laura-dern-david-lynch-birthday-tribute-3830806">德恩</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicolas-cage">尼古拉斯·凯奇，</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/edgar-wright">埃德加·赖特</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james-gunn">詹姆斯·冈恩</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hugh-jackman">休·杰克曼</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-corgan">比利·科根</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/questlove">Questlove</a> ，您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-dies-aged-78-3829681">在这里看到更多的贡品</a>。</p><p>林奇（Lynch）的粉丝也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-fans-celebrate-late-director-on-his-79th-birthday-long-live-the-greatest-3830502">很快向他致敬</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynch-fans-hold-worldwide-group-meditation-to-honour-late-directors-legacy-3830534">有些人凭着“全球冥想”</a>旨在荣誉，而 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/gaming-industry-pays-tribute-to-david-lynch-3830370">游戏行业的数字</a>也发布了导演对历史上一些最受欢迎的游戏的影响。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/david-lynch-obituary-twin-peaks-3829834"><em>NME向已故导演的</em>致敬</a>中，马克·博蒙特（Mark Beaumont）写道，“非常&#39;lynchian&#39;一词 - 表示一种狂欢节的黑暗超现实主义； sometimes fantastical, sometimes macabre, sometimes dreamlike, often eerily everyday – will forever pay tribute to the work of one of cinema&#39;s finest ever auteurs.”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/david-lynchs-cause-of-death-has-been-revealed-3836185">David Lynch&#39;s cause of death has been revealed</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
